<plot>Filmmaker Kaz Gamble shares a first-hand portrait of his brother's struggle in this humorous yet heartbreaking documentary about growing up with undiagnosed Asperger's Syndrome. MY BROTHER TOM, follows Kaz's misunderstood and isolated brother until his family discovers a form of autism the world is only beginning to recognize.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?383459</url></doc>
